-- =============================================
-- SECTION-SUBJECTS MAPPING - OPTIMIZED DISTRIBUTION
-- Separated from 015_sample_data_8_sections.sql for easier maintenance
-- =============================================
-- Each section: 5 theory + 3 lab = 8 subjects
-- Total: 15 sections × 8 subjects = 120 mappings
-- 
-- OPTIMIZED DISTRIBUTION STRATEGY:
-- Instead of F007+F008 only handling theory (200%+ overload),
-- we assign 1 theory subject to each lab faculty (F001-F004)!
-- 
-- NEW DISTRIBUTION:
--   CSE: F007 teaches DS (1 subject) - anchor theory faculty
--        F001 teaches DBMS + DBMS Lab (theory + lab)
--        F002 teaches OS + DS Lab (theory + lab)
--        F003 teaches CN + CN Lab (theory + lab)
--        F004 teaches SE + backup labs
--        F005/F006 backup labs only
--
--   IT:  F007 teaches Web Tech (1 subject) - anchor theory faculty  
--        F001 teaches Cloud + Web Lab (theory + lab)
--        F002 teaches Cyber Sec + Cloud Lab (theory + lab)
--        F003 teaches ML + ML Lab (theory + lab)
--        F004 teaches Big Data + backup labs
--        F005/F006 backup labs only
--
-- FACULTY LOAD CALCULATION (optimized):
--   F007: 1 theory × 8 sections × 4 periods = 32 periods (67%)
--   F001-F004: 1 theory × 8 sections + 4 labs × 4 periods = 48 periods (100%)
-- =============================================

-- Clear existing section_subjects data
